---
title: Roasted Aubergine Noodles with Garlicky Greens and Crushed Peanuts
description: Our Roasted Aubergine Noodles are a delicious veggie option that make it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-aubergine-noodles-a4c3516e-89bb215c.jpg
